# Keep the Docker build context clean — Dockerfile.prod runs `npm ci` itself,
# so the local node_modules must never ride along (2026-06-12: Finder-duplicated
# "@types/* 2" dirs in local node_modules were copied into the image and broke
# `vue-tsc` with TS2688 during `npm run build`).
node_modules
dist
.vite
*.log
.DS_Store
